column3: “great weed, feel high right away after first bowl and last longer than usual weed. Definitely recommend!”
“Just got some of this recently and it's very nice. Perfect mix of head and body. High seems long lasting to me. Recommend!”
“An excellent strain!! Wonderful aroma, tastes great and the effects are just as described. Definitely one of my new favorites!!”
